                        <div class="timeline-panel">
                            <div class="timeline-heading">
                                <h4>Tips two</h4>
                                <h4 class="subheading">Louisa May Alcott</h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-body"><p class="text-muted">Good books, like good friends, are few and chosen; the more select, the more enjoyable. </p></div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="timeline-image"><img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="../assets/img/about/3.jpg" alt="" /></div>
                        <div class="timeline-panel">
                            <div class="timeline-heading">
                                <h4>Tips three</h4>
                                <h4 class="subheading">Rene Descartes</h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-body"><p class="text-muted">The reading of all good books is like a conversation with the finest minds of past centuries.</p>

                            </p></div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="timeline-inverted">
                        <div class="timeline-image"><img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="../assets/img/about/4.jpg" alt="" /></div>
                        <div class="timeline-panel">
                            <div class="timeline-heading">
                                <h4>Tips four</h4>
                                <h4 class="subheading">Dr Seuss</h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-body"><p class="text-muted">The more that you read, the more things you will know. The more that you learn, the more places youâ€™ll go. </p></div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="timeline-inverted">
                        <div class="timeline-image">
                            <h4>
                                Be Part
                                <br />
                                Of Our
